US-Mexican authorities shut tunnel linked to El Chapo cartel 
The Telegraph Friday 23rd October, 2015 
Authorities on both sides of the U.S.-Mexico border have shut the 10th drug-smuggling tunnel to San Diego in more than a decade, a passageway Mexican authorities on Thursday attributed to the cartel of fugitive kingpin...
